            <title><![CDATA[秦刚两会记者会首秀 回答问题较去年减近半]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2023-03/image_20230307_122249_355.jpeg?VersionId=upW25Fr8c0nhrCjdRIUKagHvG0huRyHc&amp;itok=M3fzjNUm" title="中国外长秦刚在记者会回应问题期间至少九次喝水。（黄小芳摄）" alt="中国外长秦刚在记者会回应问题期间至少九次喝水。（黄小芳摄）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2023-03/image_20230307_122249_355.jpeg?VersionId=upW25Fr8c0nhrCjdRIUKagHvG0huRyHc&amp;itok=M3fzjNUm" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
